title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Learning a new skill or procedure boosts your confidence today. You naturally enjoy uncovering methods to be more effective at what you do, even if its just for fun. The fastidious Virgo Moon in your 9th House of Expansion is stimulated by ingenious Uranus, pushing the boundaries of what you know. But you must cast aside your insecurities if you dont feel like the most promising pupil. Trust the process more than your fear of how things look. Knowledge prompts you to stand on the ledge of your ignorance and leap. The more you know, the more you grow. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
